## Auto detect text files and perform LF normalization
* text=auto

## DOCUMENTS
*.md text
*.rst text

## CONFIG
*.ini text
*.config text
*.conf text
*.yaml text eof=lf
*.yml text eof=lf
*.tpl text
*.xml text
*.tmpl text eof=lf
*.j2 text
.gitattributes text
.gitignore text
.dockerignore text
.yamllint text eof=lf
.ansible-lint text eof=lf
Vagrantfile text diff=ruby
.mailmap text

## ARCHIVES
*.7z  binary
